column1: # Church and Station directions put the initial site in the northern part of Holme Hall grounds, near the vicarage.
# The initial observer (Mr Pybus) retired from recording in March 1946. Rev. Shepherd resumed readings from the vicarage in August 1946.
# Estimated readings for April-July 1946 have been omitted.
# Readings at the vicarage ended in April 1953, and the gauge moved 1/2 mile south to the Park Gates site.
# The grid reference is for the Vicarage.
